cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper involves computer vision and machine learning techniques for detecting hazards in supermarkets. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques for hazard detection, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the development of a hazard detection dataset, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of ensuring clean and safe environments, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
